fixPdbXrefs(EnzymeModel) - Method in class uk.ac.ebi.ep.adapter.uniprot.AbstractUniprotCallable
Fixes any cross references to PDB by querying the mega-map, which only contains PDB entries from empirical methods, no theoretical models.
Note that this method will do nothing if no MegaMapper is set for this UniprotCallable.
